abstract: >-
  A systematic physics-based assessment of reported UAP flight characteristics,
  evaluating whether known or theoretically plausible mechanisms—including
  Alcubierre warp metrics, nuclear fusion, and metamaterials—could account for
  the Five Observables taxonomy. Concludes that barriers are primarily materials
  science maturity, not fundamental physics violations.
